name: French Acrylic Cuff
description: In neon pink and green , handmade in France and imported by Chaos NY. We saw them and instantly fell in love.Expensive? Yes.  Worth it?  Absolutely!

name: Dinamal Bear
description:
Creations that are unique to Chaos NY, all Dinamals are handmade from recycled fabrics. Lovingly created by our Production Manager Dina Reis, they are inspired from the toys of Patricias childhood made just as lovingly by her grandmother.

Note: While not two Dinamals are ever alike we will try and honor a color request.

name: Small Felt Rose Ring
description:
Handmade by Swiss artist Karin Wagner, these small felt rings in bold colors with luscious petals are a real showstopper.

One size fits most.

Available colors: Orange, Fuchsia, Turquoise, Yellow and Red.

name: Large Felt Rose Ring
description:
Handmade by Swiss artist Karin Wagner, these large felt rings in bold colors with luscious petals are a real showstopper.

Available colors: Lime, Turquoise, Light Pink, Heather Brown, Red, Orange, Royal Blue, White and Fuchsia.

One size fits most.

name: Necklace with Felt Balls and Flowers
description:
Hand-made by Swiss artist Karin Wagner this necklace on black elastic cord with multiple hand-felted balls and flower stations gives this magnificent piece the airy feeling of spring. May be worn as a lariat, a chocker or as a bracelet.

Length: 60.

Available colors: Red, Green, Pink; flowers are white with green leaves.

name: Necklace with Felt Balls
description:
Swiss artist Karin Wagners jewelry is unique and eye-catching. In this necklace, referred to by Elena as her pearls, an elastic cord is sprinkled with dozens of small hand-felted balls. It may be worn either as a lariat or wrapped around the neck several times to form a chocker. Wrapped around the wrist this piece can even serve as a multi-strand bracelet. Its so lightweight youll forget youre wearing it; however, you will be reminded by the multitude of compliments received.

Length: 60.

Available colors: Red, Black, Yellow, Turquoise, White, Orange and Pink. Elastic cord is black for all necklaces.

name: Felt Poppy Brooch
description:
Handmade by Swiss artist Karin Wagner, this brooch emulates a real poppy flower with a touch of contrasting color on the bud. The rich colors of the petals make this a stand-out accessory for any item in your wardrobe.

Width: 41/4 

Available Colors: Red, Turquoise, Orange, Yellow, Royal Blue, Fuchsia and Heather Brown.

name: Felt Poppy Ring
description:
Handmade by Swiss artist Karin Wagner, this felt poppy ring stands high off the hand (1 inch) providing a huge burst of color with a contrasting bud. While this piece will never go unnoticed, its weightlessness will make you forget you have it on.

Width: 31/4

One size fits most.

Available Colors: Orange, Red, Blue, Turquoise, Yellow, Fuchsia and Brown.
